- rgb_color	// Stores as integral 0..255
- hsv_color
- device_color (or uvec_color, vec_color, ivec_color..) // these are RGB(A)

=> Converting constructors! (to glm::uvec3...)
	to_uvec(), to_ivec(), to_vec() // last one: 0.0..1.0 vector
	to_uvec4(), to_ivec4(), to_vec4() // with alpha=1.0
		=> these only on rgb_color
		
